<!--
  Sparkle appcast feed for grapfel.
  Hosted at: https://sfegette.github.io/grapfel/appcast.xml

  One-time setup:
  1. In your GitHub repo → Settings → Pages → Source: "Deploy from a branch"
     Branch: main, Folder: /docs → Save.
  2. Generate your EdDSA key pair (run once, from repo root):
       ./path/to/Sparkle/bin/generate_keys
     Or download Sparkle's release package and use the included generate_keys binary.
     Store the private key in Keychain (generate_keys does this automatically).
  3. Copy the printed public key into Info.plist → SUPublicEDKey.

  Items are prepended here by Scripts/release.sh on each release.
-->
